Show all connected devices

```
fdisk -l
```

Add partition

```
fdisk path
> n (for "new")
> d (for default)
> w (for write
```

format device as ext4

```
mkfs -t ext4 /dev/sda1
```

mount

```
mkdir /volume
mount  /dev/sda1 /volume
chmod 777 -R /volume
```

list all free space (test)
```
df -h
```
